@startuml
actor User
participant "CLI / DiaryController" as DC
participant "AiServiceImpl" as AI
participant "KnowledgeBaseLoader" as KB
participant "CrisisDetector" as CD

User -> DC: Submits Thought Diary entry
DC -> CD: detectCrisis(thought)
CD --> DC: CrisisAssessmentResult
DC -> AI: analyzeThought(thought)
AI -> KB: findMatchingEntries(thought)
KB --> AI: List<CbtKnowledgeEntry>
AI --> DC: ThoughtAnalysisResponse
DC -> User: Shows analysis & reframing prompts
@enduml
